  franz reichelt , also known as frantz reichelt or françois reichelt ( 1879 – february 4 , 1912 ) , was an austrian - born french tailor , inventor and parachuting pioneer , now sometimes referred to as the flying tailor , who is remembered for jumping to his death from the eiffel tower while testing a wearable parachute of his own design .

what a way to go : franz reichelt died after a 1912 jump from this tall parisian structure testing his parachute - overcoat combo

